name: fsevents
notes: Native module (C++ bindings via node-gyp) for macOS filesystem event watching. Uses FSEvents API to monitor file/directory changes on macOS. Optional dependency in many build tools (chokidar, webpack, vite) for improved file watching performance on macOS - gracefully degrades to polling on other platforms. Similar native file watchers: sane (Facebook's file watcher), watchman (Facebook's file watching service). Not applicable to Workers - native modules with C++ bindings cannot run in serverless JavaScript environment.
